author: ian_dickinson
msg: Moved list support from ontology.OntList to rdf.model.RDFList. Removed
all dependencies on ontology package from RDF list. Changed semantics
of add and concatenate to fail with an exception if an update is attempted
on the empty (rdf:nil) list. Added with() operation with the semantics of
the old add() (i.e. it returns the updated list).
